  - ZoneId: drowned_market
    DisplayName: The Drowned Market
    QuestName: Silence the Drowned Market
    Description: The drowned dead haunt the flooded market NORTH of the hub. Lay
      all four hauntings to rest, then return SOUTH to Council Hall.
    RequiredEncounters: 4
    XpEach: 900
    Gold: 250
    PrerequisiteZoneIds:
    - old_docks
    StartsAvailable: 0
    FinalQuest: 0
  - ZoneId: sunken_warcamp
    DisplayName: The Sunken Warcamp
    QuestName: The Warband Below
    Description: Karg Splitjaw's orc warband holds the sunken quarter SOUTH of the
      walls. Break both picket bands, then storm the war-tent and slay the Warchief
      before returning to Council Hall.
    RequiredEncounters: 3
    XpEach: 1200
    Gold: 400
    PrerequisiteZoneIds:
    - drowned_market
    StartsAvailable: 0
    FinalQuest: 0
  - ZoneId: glasslit_temple
