      Lightwell. Follow the gold waypoint through the newly opened gate, seal all
      three breaches, then return SOUTHWEST to Council Hall.
    RequiredEncounters: 3
    XpEach: 1200
    Gold: 750
    PrerequisiteZoneIds:
    - glasslit_temple
    StartsAvailable: 0
